      <title>马克龙辞职传闻导致法国债券价格创 2020 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/french-yield-premium-over-germany-jumps-to-highest-since-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙决定提前举行大选后，有关他未来的谣言四起，法国债券价格暴跌，导致收益率出现自疫情爆发以来的两日最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/french-yield-premium-over-germany-jumps-to-highest-since-october</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 09:14:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
